content: Shoutout to the $XVI community for all the solid feedback. You've helped us dial in our AI to anticipate the market, not just follow it. We're planning something cool to show off this to investors, stay tuned!

Just got off a call with potential investors. They're pretty hyped about our AI's ability to adapt and predict niche market trends. They're curious about how it bounces back, so we're gearing up for a full demo to show off the magic.
